title: Scrapheap Challenge - 11x02 - Stuck In The Mud.avi
description:
Mud, mud and more mud.

"Dicks Diamonds" (Dick Strawbridge & Jim Milner with guest Andy 'Proper Job' Barnes.) challengers are "The Supermodels", "The Wreckers" and "The Criticizers".

Their challenge : to retrieve a 'bomb' from mud. 

Whichever team wins gets to take on "Dicks Diamonds".

Please help me seed & get these 'out there' - I have a max. upload speed of c. 80k/s. The more help I get the quicker everyone gets them. 

I'm adding one episode a day Mon - Fri as they air on ABC2 digital TV here in Australia. (We're getting them before the UK)
